      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 is a commercially validated CFD solver with documented SQA procedures conforming to ISO 9001:2015. Version control, regression test suite (>2400 test cases), and release validation reports are available. SQA documentation reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 requirements. Achieved Gradation 3 through availability of full regression test suite documentation exceeding MRL 2 minimum."
